articles.author: Jamie Carter
articles.title: In Photos: Full ‘Strawberry Moon’ Rise Marks Once-In-18-Years Event - Forbes
articles.description: Sky-watchers across the world were treated to a spectacular sight as the full "Strawberry Moon" rose in the east. This year it coincided with the June solstice.
articles.content:
The full moon of June known as Strawberry Moon rises over a fire lookout tower coinciding with the ... [+] summer solstice. (Photo by Marcos del Mazo/LightRocket via Getty Images)
